<abstract><t>The problem of quality analysis and advanced fault detection of  a pure light-path in a Dense Wavelength Division Multiplexing  (DWDM) optical network requires the transmission of optical  evidence related parameters along the provisioned route. In  this draft we propose an RSVP-TE based mechanism to collect and  evaluate optical evidence measured over optical nodes along the  light-path.</t></abstract>

